# Photo Manipulation under Linux

## Simple Photo Editor

### **gthumb**

* Can turn skewed pictures.
* Does not destroy metadata
* Allows to add a description, location and keywords 

## Simple Photo Viewer

### **eog** *Eye of Gnome*

* Allows viewing of all pictures in a dictionary

## Simple Image Stackr

### **chimpstackr** 

* Simple but excellent photo stacker 
* Source is available under [https://github.com/noah-peeters/ChimpStackr](https://github.com/noah-peeters/ChimpStackr)

    snap run chimpstackr